data.title: [we won't get fooled again]
data.text:
Jill and Jacqueline appeared in the 1988 Canadian film Dead Ringers playing ...oddly enough...twins.

Jacqueline was not bitten by the acting bug as bad as Jill. Jacqueline has worked with her sister on occasion in small parts, most notably in Jill's directorial debut The Acting Class.

Jacqueline is currently the Associate Article Editor for Chatelaine magazine in Ontario.
